# v03.tech Pricing Strategy
## AI App Generation Platform - Multi-Market Pricing Plan

---

## Executive Summary

v03.tech is positioned as a **full-stack AI app generation platform** targeting developers, startups, and small teams globally, with a primary focus on the Bangladesh market. The pricing strategy employs **value-based, tiered pricing** with local currency support and flexible billing options (monthly, yearly, one-time).

**Key Market Insights:**
- **USD to BDT Exchange Rate (2026):** ~122-124 BDT per 1 USD
- **Purchasing Power Parity:** Bangladesh GDP per capita (PPP) is ~$8,487 vs. USA ~$76,000 (11x difference)
- **Developer Market:** Bangladesh has a growing tech talent pool with competitive rates; remote developers earn $41k-$95k annually
- **Conversion Impact:** Offering local currency pricing increases checkout conversion by 30-50%

